  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">FORWARD/ADELANTE Puerto Rico, a fund created by the network of Puerto Rican foundations, collected and quickly distributed funds to vetted local grassroots organizations that provided direct assistance to communities affected by Hurricanes Maria and Irma. Now, longer term support will strengthen their response capacity, promote transparency in government,  equitable distribution of disaster recovery funds, and generate data to promote access to housing, jobs, and resilient communities.</narrative>
